  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Newborns</arm_group_label>
    <description>Critically ill newborns admitted to level III neonatal intensive care unit of a university hospital, who will be monitored using transpulmonary ultrasound dilution (&quot;advanced hemodynamic monitoring&quot;)</description>
